data.description: Enjoy the charm and community of the country with the convenience of living just outside Jefferson County. Welcome to this lovely 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch nestled in the Lakes of Dogwood neighborhood of Shepherdsville. A cozy front porch entry gives way to an ample living room. The kitchen beckons with its stainless-steel appliances, ready to serve up your favorite dishes in style. The primary bedroom and en suite bathroom are generously sized on the left side of the home with two bedrooms and a bath on the right. The fenced-in yard is perfect for your furry family members. Safety first - this home is on a cul-de-sac with sidewalks on both sides of each street in the neighborhood. Come visit today!
